@{b}Purpose:@{ub}
     Speaks the provided text using the Amiga speech synthesizer.

@{b}Specifications:@{ub}
     Speaks the provided text using the Amiga speech synthesizer,
     requires that speech support is enabled.

@{b}Result:@{ub}
     -

@{b}Warning:@{ub}
     -

@{b}Example:@{ub}
          /* Say something sensible. */

          SPEAK 'something sensible'


@EndNode

@Node "STOPBITS" "termRexx.guide/STOPBITS"
@Next "TEXTBUFFER"
@Prev "SPEAK"
