@{b}SERIALPREFS.OWNDEVUNITREQUEST@{ub}
     @{b}RELEASE@{ub} @{b}RELEASERETRY@{ub} @{b}IGNORE@{ub}

@{u}The MODEMPREFS object@{uu}

