@{u}The SCREENPREFS object@{uu}

   Available fields are:
@{b}SCREENPREFS.COLOURMODE@{ub}
     @{b}TWO@{ub} @{b}FOUR@{ub} @{b}EIGHT@{ub} @{b}SIXTEEN@{ub}

