@{u}The PROTOCOLPREFS object@{uu}

   This object features no fields, it contains a single line of text:
the XPR protocol options.

@{u}The TRANSLATIONPREFS object@{uu}

   Indices referring to the ascii codes range from 0 to 255, available
fields are:
@{b}TRANSLATIONPREFS.n.SEND@{ub}
     Text

@{b}TRANSLATIONPREFS.n.RECEIVE@{ub}
     Text

@{u}The FUNCTIONKEYPREFS object@{uu}

