@Node "Wanted!" "termRexx.guide/Wanted!"
@Next "Index"
@Prev "Attributes"
@Toc "Main"

@{b}@{u}Wanted!@{ub}@{uu}

   As of this writing only a single example ARexx script is included in
the `term' distribution (see the @{b}Rexx@{ub} drawer). However, it is desirable
to include more sample scripts so more users will be able to take
advantage of the ARexx interface.

   If you wish to share your scripts with the `term' user community,
send them (including documentation) to:

                             Olaf Barthel

                           Brabeckstrasse 35

                           D-30559 Hannover

                      Federal Republic of Germany

                    Internet: olsen@sourcery.han.de


@EndNode

